name: Property
definition: An attribute or characteristic of something

name: Data Property
definition: A property whose value is a literal

name: ObjectProperty
definition: A property whose value is an object

name: Unit
definition: A standard unit, usually within a governed system of units, by which a quantity can be expressed and universally understood

name: Feature Of Interest Class
definition: A type or category of Feature of Interest

name: Feature Of Interest
definition: A thing whose property is being estimated or calculated in the course of an Observation to arrive at a Result, or whose property is being manipulated by an Actuator, or which is being sampled or transformed in an act of Sampling

name: Metric
definition: A particular property of a particular feature of interest

name: Representation
definition: A rendering of an object in a different schema or format
